[package]
name = "libp2p-relay-manager"
version = "0.3.0"
edition = "2021"
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
description = "(WIP) Implementation of a relay-manager"
repository = "https://github.com/dariusc93/rust-ipfs"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "libp2p", "p2p", "networking",]
authors = [ "Darius Clark",]
exclude = [ ".gitignore",]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"
anyhow = "1.0"
futures = "0.3"
log = "0.4"
void = "1.0"
rand = "0.8"

[dependencies.libp2p]
features = [ "relay",]
version = "0.54.1"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies]

[[bin]]
name = "oku-fs"
path = "src/cli.rs"
doc = false
required-features = [ "cli",]

[package]
name = "oku-fs"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]

serde = "1.0.215"
toml = "0.8.19"
rayon = "1.10.0"
tantivy = "0.22.0"

[features]
default = []
fuse = [ "dep:libc", "dep:fuse_mt", "dep:fuser",]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.20"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.fuse_mt]
version = "0.6.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.fuser]
version = "0.13.0"

[dependencies.miette]

version = "0.11.5"

[dependencies.url]

[package]
authors = [ "Darius C", "Rust-IPFS contributors",]
rust-version = "1.80"
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

readme = "README.md"

[workspace]

[package]
name = "rust-ipns"

edition = "2021"

repository = "https://github.com/dariusc93/rust-ipfs"

version = "0.6.0"
authors = [ "Darius Clark",]
keywords = [ "libp2p", "ipfs",]

[dependencies]
cid = "0.11.1"
multihash = "0.19.2"
sha2 = "0.10.8"

[features]
default = [ "libp2p",]

[dependencies.cbor4ii]

[dependencies.quick-protobuf]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.35"

[dependencies.derive_more]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.getrandom]

version = "0.2.15"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies.clap]

[dependencies.ticky]
